%% ActivaClub - Post-Login Role Redirect + Route Guards (AC-009)
%% Diagram 5 of 8
%% Last updated: 2026-04-05

sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant Zustand as Zustand Store

    Note over User,Zustand: After successful OTP verification (verify-otp returns 200)

    Frontend->>Zustand: Read IdToken
    Frontend->>Frontend: Decode IdToken payload (Base64url)
    Frontend->>Frontend: Extract cognito:groups claim

    alt cognito:groups contains "Admin"
        Frontend->>Zustand: Set role = "Admin"
        Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /admin/dashboard
    else cognito:groups contains "Manager"
        Frontend->>Zustand: Set role = "Manager"
        Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /admin/dashboard
    else cognito:groups contains "Member" or claim absent
        Frontend->>Zustand: Set role = "Member"
        Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /member/dashboard
    else Decode error or unexpected value
        Frontend->>Zustand: Set role = "Member" (safe fallback)
        Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /member/dashboard
        Note over Frontend: Warning logged to console
    end

    Note over User,Zustand: Route guard on every protected route (PrivateRoute)

    User->>Frontend: Navigate to /admin/dashboard
    Frontend->>Zustand: Read role
    alt role is "Admin" or "Manager"
        Frontend->>Frontend: Render /admin/dashboard
    else role is "Member"
        Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /member/dashboard
    else Not authenticated
        Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /login
    end

    User->>Frontend: Navigate to /member/dashboard
    Frontend->>Zustand: Read role
    alt role is "Member"
        Frontend->>Frontend: Render /member/dashboard
    else Not authenticated
        Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /login
    end
